    eiconséxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/com/github/corna.Vivado/07ad2cd5a0a53383dce2081f799f9726/icons/128x128/com.github.corna.Vivado.pngxühttps://dl.flathub.org/media/com/github/corna.Vivado/07ad2cd5a0a53383dce2081f799f9726/icons/128x128@2/com.github.corna.Vivado.pngkscreenshotsüxrhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/com/github/corna.Vivado/07ad2cd5a0a53383dce2081f799f9726/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesoDevelopment,IDEprich_descriptiony¡Vivado Design Suite is a software suite designed by Xilinx for the design, synthesis and analysis of HDL for its line of FPGAs and SoCs. Vivado Design Suite includes many tools, like Vivado, Vitis, Vitis HLS and many others. This package provides a flatpak wrapper over an official installation. As the Xilinx tools are not redistributable, this package does not contain any Xilinx-licensed material, which is instead downloaded on-the-fly through the official Xilinx installer. To install it, install the flatpak package, then run any Xilinx launcher and follow the instructions. To uninstall, just remove the flatpak package to remove this wrapper. Note that this does not remove the Xilinx installation; to remove it, run the launcher &quot;Uninstall Xilinx Design Tools or Devices&quot; (or run &quot;flatpak uninstall com.github.corna.Vivado --delete-data&quot; to wipe everything in in &quot;~/.var/app/com.github.corna.Vivado/&quot;).gversione1.0.0ºfapp_idxcom.github.coslyk.MoonPlayerdnamejMoonPlayergsummaryxOVideo player for playing and downloading online videos from YouTube, Youku etc.kscreenshotsåx2https://coslyk.github.io/files/moonplayer-play.pngx6https://coslyk.github.io/files/moonplayer-explorer.pngx1https://coslyk.github.io/files/moonplayer-url.pngx5https://coslyk.github.io/files/moonplayer-danmaku.pngx6https://coslyk.github.io/files/moonplayer-download.pngx3https://coslyk.github.io/files/moonplayer-hwdec.pngjcategoriesqAudioVideo,Playerprich_descriptionxïMoonPlayer is an interesting player that lets you to enjoy videos. It c