emoteGtkdnamesTransmission Remotegsummaryx2Remotely manage the Transmission BitTorrent clienteiconséxÅhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/TransmissionRemoteGtk/f4ee9f68e9651dc27a5aa4ef408f42c7/icons/128x128/io.github.TransmissionRemoteGtk.pngxæhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/TransmissionRemoteGtk/f4ee9f68e9651dc27a5aa4ef408f42c7/icons/128x128@2/io.github.TransmissionRemoteGtk.pngkscreenshotsüxzhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/io/github/TransmissionRemoteGtk/f4ee9f68e9651dc27a5aa4ef408f42c7/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesxNetwork,FileTransfer,P2Pprich_descriptionyO
      Transmission Remote Gtk allows you to remotely manage the Transmission BitTorrent client using its RPC interface. You can use it to to manage torrents (start/stop/verify/reannounce/remove/remove and delete), add new ones (it works as a .torrent fle handler from a webbrowser), and configure settings on transmission-daemon.
