      This package contains Pd-L2Ork, which is a fork of Pure Data that
      bundles a lot of useful extensions, brings a modern HTML5-based
      user interface, and provides a set of unique features, including
      K12 beginner mode, and L2Ork-Tweeter. While Pd-L2Ork is backwards
      compatible with Pure Data and other variants, the same is not true
      the other way around. Hence, some of the most advanced content
      created in Pd-L2Ork may not run well, or at all on other Pure Data
      variants. Pd-L2Ork is a brainchild of the Virginia Tech Linux
      Laptop Orchestra (L2Ork).
