      OpenRA is a project that recreates and modernizes the classic Command &amp; Conquer real time strategy games. We have developed a flexible open source game engine (the OpenRA engine) that provides a common platform for rebuilding and reimagining classic 2D and 2.5D RTS games (the OpenRA mods).
    gversionprelease-20231010¿fapp_idx%net.opentabletdriver.OpenTabletDriverdnamepOpenTabletDrivergsummaryx!Cross-platform tablet driver tooleiconsüxøhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/opentabletdriver/OpenTabletDriver/5dc27035788d5268f6299c930bf62def/icons/128x128/net.opentabletdriver.OpenTabletDriver.pngkscreenshotsâxÇhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/opentabletdriver/OpenTabletDriver/5dc27035788d5268f6299c930bf62def/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxÇhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/opentabletdriver/OpenTabletDriver/5dc27035788d5268f6299c930bf62def/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxÇhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/opentabletdriver/OpenTabletDriver/5dc27035788d5268f6299c930bf62def/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategorieshSettingsprich_descriptionxÓOpenTabletDriver is an open source, cross platform, user mode tablet driver. The goal of OpenTabletDriver is to be cross platform as possible with the highest compatibility in an easily configurable graphical user interface.gversionhv0.6.4.0¿fapp_idsnet.oz9aec.GpredictdnamehGpredictgsummaryx9Real-time satellite tracking and orbit prediction programeiconsüxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/oz9aec/Gpredict/31709aabc4a82b6e64f11c6789255896/icons/128x128/net.oz9aec.Gpredict.pngkscreenshotsüxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/oz9aec/Gpredict/31709aabc4a82b6e64f11c6789255896/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesx,Astronomy,Education,HamRadio,Network,Scienceprich_descriptionxgGpredict is a real time satellite tracking and orbit prediction program written using the Gtk+ widgets.gversiong2.3.115¿fapp_idonet.pcsx2.PCSX2dnameePCSX2gsummaryvPlayStation 2 Emulatoreiconsüxohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/pcsx2/PCSX2/6d5e6671646868c8cbcc24b5c7121918/icons/128x128/net.pcsx2.PCSX2.pngkscreenshotséxjhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/pcsx2/PCSX2/6d5e6671646868c8cbcc24b5c7121918/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxjhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/pcsx2/PCSX2/6d5e6671646868c8cbcc24b5c7121918/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngjcategoriesmGame,Emulatorprich_descriptionyPPCSX2 is a free and open-source PlayStation 2 (PS2) emulator. Its purpose is to emulate the PS2&apos;s hardware, using a combination of MIPS CPU Interpreters, Recompilers, and a Virtual Machine which manages hardware states and PS2 system memory. This allows you to play PS2 games on your PC, with many additional features and benefits.gversionhv2.1.226¿fapp_idxnet.peercoin.peercoin-qtdnamehPeercoingsummaryx0Peercoin, a green crypto for sustainable future.eiconséxühttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/peercoin/peercoin-qt/e555e2766e3e619497f6a6daee0b37cf/icons/128x128/net.peercoin.peercoin-qt.pngxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/peercoin/peercoin-qt/e555e2766e3e619497f6a6daee0b37cf/icons/128x128@2/net.peercoin.peercoin-qt.pngkscreenshotsüxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/peercoin/peercoin-qt/e555e2766e3e619497f6a6daee0b37cf/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesgNetworkprich_descriptiony6
      Peercoin, launched in August 2012, is the world&apos;s first cryptocoin secured by Proof of Stake.
      It stands as an energy-efficient digital store of value, enabling online transactions without relying on a central authority.
      Its efficient design allows for transaction validation even on basic hardware like the first-generation Raspberry Pi.
