    gversione1.6.0ºfapp_idx#net.sourceforge.jpdftweak.jPdfTweakdnamejjPDF TweakgsummaryxSwiss Army Knife for PDF fileskscreenshotsüxjhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/flathub/net.sourceforge.jpdftweak.jPdfTweak/master/img/screenshot-01.pngjcategoriesoGraphics,Officeprich_descriptionxëjPDF Tweak is a Java Swing application that can combine, split, rotate, reorder, watermark, encrypt, sign, and otherwise tweak PDF files.gversionc1.1ºfapp_idxnet.sourceforge.kmetronomednamesDrumstick Metronomegsummaryx4Drumstick MIDI Metronome based on the ALSA Sequencerkscreenshotséx8https://kmetronome.sourceforge.io/images/kmetronome1.pngx8https://kmetronome.sourceforge.io/images/kmetronome2.pngjcategoriesx%Audio,AudioVideo,Education,Midi,Musicprich_descriptionyQDrumstick Metronome is a MIDI metronome with Qt5 interface, based on the ALSA sequencer. Intended for musicians and music students, it is a tool to keep the rhythm while playing musical instruments. It uses MIDI for sound generation instead of digital audio, allowing low CPU usage, and very accurate timing thanks to the ALSA sequencer.gversione1.4.0ºfapp_idxnet.sourceforge.kmidimondnamevDrumstick MIDI MonitorgsummaryxGDrumstick MIDI Monitor is a MIDI monitor for Linux using ALSA sequencerkscreenshotsäx4https://kmidimon.sourceforge.io/images/kmidimon1.pngx4https://kmidimon.sourceforge.io/images/kmidimon2.pngx4https://kmidimon.sourceforge.io/images/kmidimon3.pngx4https://kmidimon.sourceforge.io/images/kmidimon4.pngjcategoriesuAudio,AudioVideo,Midiprich_descriptiony└Drumstick MIDI Monitor logs MIDI events coming from MIDI external ports or applications via the ALSA sequencer, and from SMF (Standard MIDI files) or WRK (Cakewalk/Sonar) files. It is especially useful if you want to debug MIDI software or your MIDI setup. It features a nice graphical user interface, customizable event filters and sequencer parameters, support for MIDI and ALSA messages, and saving the recorded event list to a SMF or text file.gversione1.4.0¿fapp_idx"net.sourceforge.lgames.LBreakoutHDdnamekLBreakoutHDgsummaryxArkanoid / Breakout alike gameeiconsüxòhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LBreakoutHD/fe5379b5f97a93871d2034d2c42a0f51/icons/128x128/net.sourceforge.lgames.LBreakoutHD.pngkscreenshotsâx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LBreakoutHD/fe5379b5f97a93871d2034d2c42a0f51/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LBreakoutHD/fe5379b5f97a93871d2034d2c42a0f51/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LBreakoutHD/fe5379b5f97a93871d2034d2c42a0f51/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionxDLBreakoutHD is a clone of popular games such as Arkanoid or Breakoutgversione1.1.9¿fapp_idxnet.sourceforge.lgames.LGeneraldnamehLGeneralgsummaryx5Turn based strategy game engine (like Panzer General)ncontent_ratingxQ
