    kscreenshotsâx.https://lgames.sourceforge.io/LGeneral/ss0.jpgx.https://lgames.sourceforge.io/LGeneral/ss1.jpgx.https://lgames.sourceforge.io/LGeneral/ss2.jpgjcategoriesqGame,StrategyGameprich_descriptionyyLGeneral is a turn-based strategy engine heavily inspired by Panzer General. You play single scenarios or whole campaigns turn by turn against a human player or the AI. Entrenchment, rugged defense, defensive fire, surprise contacts, surrender, unit supply, weather influence, reinforcements and other implementations contribute to the tactical and strategic depth of the game.gversione1.4.4¿fapp_idxnet.sourceforge.lgames.LPairs2dnamegLPairs2gsummarysClassic memory gameeiconsüxìhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LPairs2/55bcedd2537f1c2702960e8e3c0b831a/icons/128x128/net.sourceforge.lgames.LPairs2.pngkscreenshotsâxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LPairs2/55bcedd2537f1c2702960e8e3c0b831a/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LPairs2/55bcedd2537f1c2702960e8e3c0b831a/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LPairs2/55bcedd2537f1c2702960e8e3c0b831a/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionxÓLPairs2 is a classic memory game where you turn over any two cards and if they match they get removed. The game is over when all cards have been matched. You can also try to match triplets and quadruplets (fun, but hard...).gversione2.3.1¿fapp_idxnet.sourceforge.lgames.LTrisdnameeltrisgsummaryx!Game of skill with falling blockseiconsüxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LTris/43cf4f525c41ad6387edf2f2c14dbafe/icons/128x128/net.sourceforge.lgames.LTris.pngkscreenshotsâxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LTris/43cf4f525c41ad6387edf2f2c14dbafe/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LTris/43cf4f525c41ad6387edf2f2c14dbafe/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/lgames.LTris/43cf4f525c41ad6387edf2f2c14dbafe/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionyM
          LTris as a tetris clone: differently shaped blocks are falling down
          the rectangular playing field and can be moved sideways or rotated by
