    Molsketch is a program for drawing two-dimensional schematic representations of molecules. The goal of the program is to make this quick and easy, without sacrificing the resulting quality. Of course your creations can be used afterwards as vector or bitmap image in any document, presentation or website. Some of the features of Molsketch are:
    gversione0.8.1¿fapp_idtnet.sourceforge.osmodnamedOsmogsummaryrPersonal organizereiconséxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/osmo/7e76ebc29236ffcd7d2e517320d78e14/icons/128x128/net.sourceforge.osmo.pngx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/osmo/7e76ebc29236ffcd7d2e517320d78e14/icons/128x128@2/net.sourceforge.osmo.pngkscreenshotsâxohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/osmo/7e76ebc29236ffcd7d2e517320d78e14/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/osmo/7e76ebc29236ffcd7d2e517320d78e14/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/net/sourceforge/osmo/7e76ebc29236ffcd7d2e517320d78e14/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesx!Office,Calendar,ContactManagementprich_descriptionyòOsmo is a handy personal organizer which includes calendar, tasks manager and
address book modules. It was designed to be a small, easy to use and good
looking PIM tool to help to manage personal information. In current state the
organizer is quite convenient in use - for example, user can perform nearly
all operations using keyboard. Also, a lot of parameters are configurable to
meet user preferences.gversione0.4.4ºfapp_idxnet.sourceforge.paulstretchdnamekpaulstretchgsummaryxêThis is a program for extreme sound stretching (like 50x) and for applying special effects by &quot;spectral smoothing&quot; the sounds.kscreenshotsäx?https://hypermammut.sourceforge.net/paulstretch/screenshot1.pngx?https://hypermammut.sourceforge.net/paulstretch/screenshot3.pngx?https://hypermammut.sourceforge.net/paulstretch/screenshot2.pngx?https://hypermammut.sourceforge.net/paulstretch/screenshot4.pngjcategoriespAudio,AudioVideoprich_descriptiony/It can transform any sound/music to a texture. Please note that this is suitable only for extreme time stretching (e.g. if have a melody of 3 minutes and you want to listen it in 3 hours). If you want &quot;less extreme&quot; time stretching, you can use a program which contains the SoundTouch library.gversione2.2-2ºfapp_idxnet.sourceforge.pdfchaindnameiPDF ChaingsummaryxCPDF Chain is a graphical user interface for the PDF Toolkit (PDFtk)kscreenshotsåxIhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/pdfchain/screenshots/329661.jpg/max/max/1xIhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/pdfchain/screenshots/329669.jpg/max/max/1xIhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/pdfchain/screenshots/329671.jpg/max/max/1xIhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/pdfchain/screenshots/329663.jpg/max/max/1xIhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/pdfchain/screenshots/329659.jpg/max/max/1xIhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/pdfchain/screenshots/329673.jpg/max/max/1jcategoriesfOfficeprich_descriptionx³If PDF is electronic paper, then PDFtk is an electronic staple-remover, hole-punch, binder, secret-decoder-ring, and X-Ray-glasses. PDFtk is a simple tool for doing everyday things with PDF documents, and PDF Chain is a nice frontend application to it.gversiong0.4.4.2ºfapp_idx net.sourceforge.projectM.desktopdnamehprojectMgsummaryxJMusic visualizer which uses 3D accelerated iterative image based renderingkscreenshotsâx®https://raw.githubusercontent.com/projectM-visualizer/projectm/v3.1.12/src/projectM-MusicPlugin/projectM%20screenshots/Screen%20Shot%202014-07-18%20at%202.14.41%20PM.pngx®https://raw.githubusercontent.com/projectM-visualizer/projectm/v3.1.12/src/projectM-MusicPlugin/projectM%20screenshots/Screen%20Shot%202014-07-18%20at%202.13.53%20PM.pngx®https://raw.githubusercontent.com/projectM-visualizer/projectm/v3.1.12/src/projectM-MusicPlugin/projectM%20screenshots/Screen%20Shot%202014-07-18%20at%202.15.36%20PM.pngjcategoriespAudio,AudioVideoprich_descriptionxKMusic visualizer which uses 3D accelerated iterative image based rendering.gversionf3.1.12ºfapp_idx%net.sourceforge.qtpfsgui.LuminanceHDRdnamemLuminance HDRgsummaryqCreate HDR imageskscreenshotsäxChttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/qtpfsgui/screenshots/MainWindow.pngxAhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/qtpfsgui/screenshots/BatchHDR.pngxFhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/qtpfsgui/screenshots/MainWindow-tm.pngxBhttps://a.fsdn.com/con/app/proj/qtpfsgui/screenshots/HdrWizard.pngjcategoriesx52DGraphics,Graphics,Photography,RasterGraphics,Viewerprich_descriptionyLuminance HDR is an application for taking a set of pictures of the same scene with different exposure settings and creating a high dynamic range (HDR) image. It supports a range on input image formats, including JPEG, TIFF and RAW. It provides eleven tone mapping operators for converting the HDR back to a low dynamic range image (LDR). It can also rotate, crop, resize HDR images and apply projective transformations. HDR images can be created and tone mapped in batch and a tool is provided for copying EXIF data from/to a set of images.gversiong2.6.1.1®fapp_idx%net.sourceforge.quakespasm.QuakespasmdnamejQuakespasmgsummaryx*A modern port of the original Quake enginencontent_ratingxÝ
