ocore.CorePDFdnamegCorePDFgsummaryxA simple lightweight PDF viewereiconséxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/cubocore/CorePDF/5c414c4a1d3a449e35146e2fdca533de/icons/128x128/org.cubocore.CorePDF.pngx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/cubocore/CorePDF/5c414c4a1d3a449e35146e2fdca533de/icons/128x128@2/org.cubocore.CorePDF.pngkscreenshotsüxohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/cubocore/CorePDF/5c414c4a1d3a449e35146e2fdca533de/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesrOffice,Qt,X-CSuiteprich_descriptionx^
