    kscreenshotsüx4http://www.freecol.org/images/screen-0.8.0-large.jpgjcategoriesqGame,StrategyGameprich_descriptionyÌThe FreeCol team aims to create an Open Source version of Colonization (released under the GPL). At first we&apos;ll try to make an exact clone of Colonization. The visuals will be brought up to date with more recent standards but will remain clean, simple and functional. Certain new &apos;features&apos; will be implemented but the gameplay and the rules will be exactly the same as the original game. Examples of modern features are: an isometric map and multiplayer support.gversione1.1.0¿fapp_idvorg.freedesktop.BustlednamefBustlegsummaryxVisualize D-Bus activityeiconséx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/freedesktop/Bustle/feb56b1eae702522f1fc813c892de17d/icons/128x128/org.freedesktop.Bustle.pngxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/freedesktop/Bustle/feb56b1eae702522f1fc813c892de17d/icons/128x128@2/org.freedesktop.Bustle.pngkscreenshotsâxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/freedesktop/Bustle/feb56b1eae702522f1fc813c892de17d/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/freedesktop/Bustle/feb56b1eae702522f1fc813c892de17d/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/freedesktop/Bustle/feb56b1eae702522f1fc813c892de17d/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesxDevelopment,Debugger,Profilingprich_descriptiony▀Bustle draws sequence diagrams of D-Bus activity.
