    gversionc4.3ºfapp_idxorg.goldcoinproject.goldcoin-qtdnamehGoldcoingsummaryx/Discover the Gold Standard of Digital Currency.kscreenshotsüxPhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/expatjedi/flatpak-data/main/wallets_splash.pngjcategoriesnFinance,Officeprich_descriptiony─Goldcoin is the first Digital Gold. A super secure value store and cash payment system. Fully decentralized and distributed. Fast and Free. It&apos;s the Money for a New Generation. Nakamoto used the word Gold multiple times in his Bitcoin whitepaper to describe the inner workings of his original protocol. We&apos;ve preserved it, improved it, and made it stronger and faster. Goldcoin (GLC) represents economic freedom to 8 billion people Worldwide.gversionf0.15.0¿fapp_idxorg.goldendict.GoldenDictdnamejGoldenDictgsummaryxDictionary lookup programeiconsüxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/goldendict/GoldenDict/fa81d0184c51e5c9aa022bbd52660069/icons/128x128/org.goldendict.GoldenDict.pngkscreenshotsàxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/goldendict/GoldenDict/fa81d0184c51e5c9aa022bbd52660069/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/goldendict/GoldenDict/fa81d0184c51e5c9aa022bbd52660069/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/goldendict/GoldenDict/fa81d0184c51e5c9aa022bbd52660069/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/goldendict/GoldenDict/fa81d0184c51e5c9aa022bbd52660069/screenshots/image-4_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/goldendict/GoldenDict/fa81d0184c51e5c9aa022bbd52660069/screenshots/image-5_orig.pngjcategoriesxOffice,Dictionary,Educationprich_descriptionyà
        GoldenDict is a feature-rich dictionary lookup program, supporting multiple
        dictionary formats (StarDict/Babylon/Lingvo/Dictd/AARD/MDict/SDict) and
        online dictionaries, featuring perfect article rendering with the complete
        markup, illustrations and other content retained, and allowing you to type
        in words without any accents or correct case.
    gversionr1.5.0RC2 (97d879e)¿fapp_idxorg.gottcode.ConnectagramdnamelConnectagramgsummaryx#Unscramble words placed in patternseiconséxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Connectagram/7d6377abdcb1682ddb23c42c6c3d2492/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.Connectagram.pngxàhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Connectagram/7d6377abdcb1682ddb23c42c6c3d2492/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.Connectagram.pngkscreenshotsüxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Connectagram/7d6377abdcb1682ddb23c42c6c3d2492/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesnGame,LogicGameprich_descriptiony¿Connectagram is a word unscrambling game. The board consists of several scrambled words that are joined together. You can choose the length of the words, the amount of words, and the pattern that the words are arranged in. The game provides a hint option for times when you are stuck, and features an online word lookup that fetches the definitions of each word from Wiktionary. Your current progress is automatically saved.gversione1.3.5¿fapp_iduorg.gottcode.CuteMazednamehCuteMazegsummaryvFind targets in a mazeeiconséx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/CuteMaze/8d875019f52c3e824896494fdd044399/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.CuteMaze.pngx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/CuteMaze/8d875019f52c3e824896494fdd044399/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.CuteMaze.pngkscreenshotsüxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/CuteMaze/8d875019f52c3e824896494fdd044399/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesnGame,LogicGameprich_descriptionyCuteMaze is a simple, top-down game in which mazes are randomly generated using one of a choice of several different algorithms. You move the character through the maze while hunting for targets (cheese, by default)ÔÇöthe game is won once all of these targets have been picked up.gversione1.3.3¿fapp_idxorg.gottcode.FocusWriterdnamekFocusWritergsummaryxFullscreen word processoreiconséxühttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/FocusWriter/c78e22fb4802a2e47453802cb55b93b9/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.FocusWriter.pngxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/FocusWriter/c78e22fb4802a2e47453802cb55b93b9/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.FocusWriter.pngkscreenshotsüxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/FocusWriter/c78e22fb4802a2e47453802cb55b93b9/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriestOffice,WordProcessorprich_descriptionyOFocusWriter is &apos;n eenvoudige woordverwerker sonder enige afleidings. Dit maak gebruik van &apos;n wegsteek-koppelvlak wat jy kan gebruik deur jou muis na die kante van die skerm te beweeg en verskaf sodoende &apos;n bekende en gebruiklike voorkoms en gevoel, terwyl die program uit jou pad bly dat jy jou in jou werk kan verdiep. gversione1.8.9¿fapp_idsorg.gottcode.GottetdnamefGottetgsummaryx!Clear the board of falling blockseiconséxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Gottet/f27059d1db7f094f27eaeeb43a047b82/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.Gottet.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Gottet/f27059d1db7f094f27eaeeb43a047b82/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.Gottet.pngkscreenshotsüxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Gottet/f27059d1db7f094f27eaeeb43a047b82/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesoGame,ArcadeGameprich_descriptionyCGottet is a falling blocks game. Pieces fall from the top of the play area and you can move them horizontally as well as rotate them before they reach the bottom of the play area. The goal is to create full lines of pieces, which are then removed. The game is over when the stack of pieces reaches the top of the play area.gversione1.2.4¿fapp_iduorg.gottcode.HexalatednamehHexalategsummaryxSpin circles to match colorseiconsüx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Hexalate/3563f0c7069413bbf5fda89de644f074/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.Hexalate.pngkscreenshotsüxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Hexalate/3563f0c7069413bbf5fda89de644f074/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesnGame,LogicGameprich_descriptionyHexalate is a color matching game. The goal of the game is to rotate and position the circles so that each touching line matches in color. You rotate circles by right clicking, and you move circles by dragging them. The game stores the positions and rotations of the circles across runs.gversione1.2.3¿fapp_idrorg.gottcode.KapowdnameqKapow Punch Clockgsummaryx$Keep track of time spent on projectseiconséxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Kapow/a452f61eaedbea76fdae5d7e727336b6/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.Kapow.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Kapow/a452f61eaedbea76fdae5d7e727336b6/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.Kapow.pngkscreenshotsäxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Kapow/a452f61eaedbea76fdae5d7e727336b6/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Kapow/a452f61eaedbea76fdae5d7e727336b6/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Kapow/a452f61eaedbea76fdae5d7e727336b6/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Kapow/a452f61eaedbea76fdae5d7e727336b6/screenshots/image-4_orig.pngjcategoriesoOffice,Calendarprich_descriptionyKapow is a punch clock program designed to easily keep track of your hours, whether you&apos;re working on one project or many. Simply clock in and out with the Start/Stop button. If you make a mistake in your hours, you can go back and edit any of the entries by double-clicking on the session in question. Kapow also allows you to easily keep track of the hours since you last billed a client, by providing a helpful &quot;Billed&quot; check box--the totals will reflect your work after the last billed session.gversione1.6.2¿fapp_idtorg.gottcode.NovProgdnamegNovProggsummaryxWordcount graphing programeiconséxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/NovProg/e18c25141efd60f3b3db93684dff59b5/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.NovProg.pngx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/NovProg/e18c25141efd60f3b3db93684dff59b5/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.NovProg.pngkscreenshotsüxohttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/NovProg/e18c25141efd60f3b3db93684dff59b5/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategorieslOffice,Chartprich_descriptiony:NovProg is a tool to graph your progress in writing a novel. You enter your wordcount and it updates a graph showing you how much progress you have made. It also shows you how far you are through your daily goal, and your total goal. Mousing over a bar in the graph will show a tooltip with that dayÔÇÖs wordcount.gversione3.2.3¿fapp_idrorg.gottcode.Peg-EdnameePeg-EgsummaryxJump pegs to eliminate themeiconséxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Peg-E/1edd720f794272f4a942d304a2e23b06/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.Peg-E.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Peg-E/1edd720f794272f4a942d304a2e23b06/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.Peg-E.pngkscreenshotsüxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Peg-E/1edd720f794272f4a942d304a2e23b06/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesnGame,BoardGameprich_descriptiony>Peg-E is a peg solitaire game in which you jump over pieces in order to remove them from the board, ultimately trying to eliminate all but one. The boards are randomly generated, with 100 levels of difficulty. The game auto-saves, and has undo-redo capability. Pieces can move horizontally, vertically, and diagonally.gversione1.3.3¿fapp_idrorg.gottcode.SimsudnameeSimsugsummaryx Fill in numbers to solve puzzleseiconséxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Simsu/76e43d023815399928a15d1a7a96991e/icons/128x128/org.gottcode.Simsu.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Simsu/76e43d023815399928a15d1a7a96991e/icons/128x128@2/org.gottcode.Simsu.pngkscreenshotsüxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/gottcode/Simsu/76e43d023815399928a15d1a7a96991e/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesnGame,LogicGameprich_descriptionySðíð©ð╝ÐüÐâ ðÁ ð┐ÐÇð¥ÐüÐéð©Ðçð║ð░ ð©ð│ÐÇð░ ð¥Ðé Ðéð©ð┐ ðíÐâð┤ð¥ð║Ðâ. ð£ð¥ðÂðÁÐéðÁ ð┤ð░ ð┐ÐÇðÁð▓ð║ð╗ÐÄÐçð▓ð░ÐéðÁ ð╝ðÁðÂð┤Ðâ Ðéð¥ð▓ð░ ð┤ð░ ð┐ð¥ð┐Ðèð╗ð▓ð░ÐéðÁ ð▒ðÁð╗ðÁðÂð║ð© (ÐÇðÁðÂð©ð╝ ÔÇ×ð╝ð¥ð╗ð©ð▓ÔÇ£) ð©ð╗ð© ð¥Ðéð│ð¥ð▓ð¥ÐÇð© (ÐÇðÁðÂð©ð╝