creenshots/image-2_orig.pngxrhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/greenfoot/Greenfoot/e9bfdcc2ab87f3d5c3eca91f1da7eb3d/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesuDevelopment,Educationprich_descriptionyOGreenfoot is an integrated development environment using Java or Stride designed primarily for educational purposes at the high school and undergraduate level. It allows easy development of two-dimensional graphical applications, such as simulations and interactive games. It is licensed under the GPL 2.0 with the Classpath Exception.gversione3.8.2¿fapp_idqorg.grisbi.GrisbidnamefGrisbigsummaryxPersonal finances managereiconséxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/grisbi/Grisbi/2fa537dd700b9e5b48f5707fa7098af8/icons/128x128/org.grisbi.Grisbi.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/grisbi/Grisbi/2fa537dd700b9e5b48f5707fa7098af8/icons/128x128@2/org.grisbi.Grisbi.pngkscreenshotsâxlhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/grisbi/Grisbi/2fa537dd700b9e5b48f5707fa7098af8/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxlhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/grisbi/Grisbi/2fa537dd700b9e5b48f5707fa7098af8/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxlhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/grisbi/Grisbi/2fa537dd700b9e5b48f5707fa7098af8/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesnOffice,Financeprich_descriptiony▄
      Grisbi is a very functional personal financial management program
      with a lot of features: checking, cash and liabilities accounts,
      several accounts with automatic contra entries, several currencies,
      including euro, arbitrary currency for every operation, money
      interchange fees, switch to euro account per account, description
      of the transactions with third parties, categories, sub-categories,
      financial year, notes, breakdown, transfers between accounts, even
      for accounts of different currencies, bank reconciliation, scheduled
      transactions, automatic recall of last transaction for every third
      party, nice and easy user interface, user manual, QIF import/export.
    gversione3.0.3¿fapp_idxorg.groestlcoin.electrum-grsdnamelElectrum-GRSgsummaryxLightweight Groestlcoin clienteiconsüxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/groestlcoin/electrum-grs/334fa4a5c6dfe89f045d977c0eebad8e/icons/128x128/org.groestlcoin.electrum-grs.pngkscreenshotsüxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/groestlcoin/electrum-grs/334fa4a5c6dfe89f045d977c0eebad8e/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesoFinance,Networkprich_descriptionx´
      Electrum-GRS&apos;s focus is speed and simplicity, with low resource usage. It uses remote servers that handle the most complicated parts of the Groestlcoin system, and it allows you to recover your wallet from a secret phrase.
    gversione4.5.4¿fapp_idxorg.groestlcoin.groestlcoin-qtdnamepGroestlcoin CoregsummaryxFFully validating Groestlcoin peer-to-peer network node, wallet and GUIeiconséxìhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/groestlcoin/groestlcoin-qt/5672838f7d9a015cad1edb3102a338dc/icons/128x128/org.groestlcoin.groestlcoin-qt.pngxÅhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/groestlcoin/groestlcoin-qt/5672838f7d9a015cad1edb3102a338dc/icons/128x128@2/org.groestlcoin.groestlcoin-qt.pngkscreenshotsüxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/groestlcoin/groestlcoin-qt/5672838f7d9a015cad1edb3102a338dc/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesxOffice,Finance,P2P,Networkprich_descriptionx├
    Groestlcoin Core connects to the Groestlcoin peer-to-peer network to download and
