symbol libraries for the KXStitch application, but other applications using similar functionality could also make use of them. There are a number of tools to aid the designing of symbols, including lines, bezier curves, rectangle and ellipse. Text characters can be selected from any font and the symbols can be mirrored or rotated. Symbols can be filled or unfilled, the line end type and joining style can be changed and the line thickness can be varied.gversione2.1.0¿fapp_idqorg.kde.akregatordnameiAkregatorgsummarywKeep up with your feedseiconséxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/kde/akregator/4e4a4193c12c51e88676a5cfb294ed45/icons/128x128/org.kde.akregator.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/kde/akregator/4e4a4193c12c51e88676a5cfb294ed45/icons/128x128@2/org.kde.akregator.pngkscreenshotsüxlhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/kde/akregator/4e4a4193c12c51e88676a5cfb294ed45/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesqNetwork,News,Feedprich_descriptionyÜ┬½Ïú┘âÏ▒┘èÏ║ÏºÏ¬┘êÏ▒┬╗ ┘ç┘ê ┘éÏºÏ▒Ïª Ï¬Ï║Ï░┘èÏºÏ¬ Ïº┘äÏúÏ«Ï¿ÏºÏ▒. ┘èÏ¬┘èÏ¡ ┘ä┘â ┬½Ïú┘âÏ▒┘èÏ║ÏºÏ¬┘êÏ▒┬╗ ┘àÏ¬ÏºÏ¿Ï╣Ï® ÏúÏ«Ï¿ÏºÏ▒ Ïº┘ä┘à┘êÏº┘éÏ╣Ïî ┘êÏº┘ä┘àÏ»┘ê┘æ┘åÏºÏ¬ ┘êÏú┘è┘æ ┘à┘êÏº┘éÏ╣ ÏúÏ«Ï▒┘ë Ï¬Ï»Ï╣┘à RSS/AtomÏî Ï░┘ä┘â ┘äÏÑ┘äÏ║ÏºÏí Ï¡ÏºÏ¼Ï® Ïº┘äÏ¬┘àÏºÏ│ Ïº┘äÏ¬┘æÏ¡Ï»┘èÏ½ÏºÏ¬ ┘èÏ»┘ê┘è┘æ┘ïÏº Ï╣Ï¿Ï▒ ┘àÏ¬ÏÁ┘ü┘æÏ¡ Ïº┘ä┘êÏ¿┘æ. ÏÁ┘Å┘à┘æ┘É┘à ┬½Ïú┘âÏ▒┘èÏ║ÏºÏ¬┘êÏ▒┬╗ ┘ä┘è┘â┘ê┘å Ï│┘ç┘ä Ïº┘äÏºÏ│Ï¬Ï«Ï»Ïº┘à ┘ê┘é┘ê┘è┘æ┘ïÏº ┘â┘üÏº┘èÏ® ┘ä┘éÏ▒ÏºÏíÏ® ┘àÏªÏºÏ¬ ┘àÏÁÏºÏ»Ï▒ Ïº┘äÏúÏ«Ï¿ÏºÏ▒ Ï¿Ï▒ÏºÏ¡Ï®. ┘â┘àÏº ┘èÏúÏ¬┘è ┘àÏ╣ Ï¬┘âÏº┘à┘ä ┬½┘â┘å┘âÏ▒┬╗ ┘äÏÑÏÂÏº┘üÏ® Ï¬Ï║Ï░┘èÏºÏ¬ Ïº┘äÏúÏ«Ï¿ÏºÏ▒ ┘êÏú┘èÏÂ┘ïÏº ┘èÏ¡Ï¬┘ê┘è ┘àÏ¬ÏÁ┘ü┘æÏ¡┘ïÏº Ï»ÏºÏ«┘ä┘è┘æ┘ïÏº ┘äÏ¬Ï│┘ç┘è┘ä ┘éÏ▒ÏºÏíÏ® Ïº┘äÏúÏ«Ï¿ÏºÏ▒.gversione6.2.3¿fapp_idqorg.kde.alligatordnameiAlligatorgsummaryxFeed reader for mobile deviceseiconséxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/kde/alligator/b002bfcf423b860330c4656866b7c3ca/icons/128x128/org.kde.alligator.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/kde/alligator/b002bfcf423b860330c4656866b7c3ca/icons/128x128@2/org.kde.alligator.pngkscreenshotséxlhttps://dl.flathub.org/