    gversione0.2.0ºfapp_idmorg.sil.BloomdnameeBloomgsummaryx7Literacy materials development for language communitieskscreenshotsäx,https://bloomlibrary.org/assets/allbooks.pngx/https://bloomlibrary.org/assets/pdfbooklets.pngx0https://bloomlibrary.org/assets/multilingual.pngx0https://bloomlibrary.org/assets/artofreading.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionyTBloom Desktop is an application that dramatically &quot;lowers the bar&quot; for language communities who want books in their own languages. Bloom delivers a low-training, high-output system where mother tongue speakers and their advocates work together to foster both community authorship and access to external material in the vernacular.gversione5.4.1¿fapp_idrorg.sil.FieldWorksdnamexFieldWorks Language Explorergsummaryx%Language and cultural data managementncontent_ratingxK
