    kscreenshotsÅxehttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/11/Lexicon_EntryBrowse-large.pngxXhttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/Sketch-large.pngxehttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/11/ConfigureDictionary-large.pngxghttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/Lexicon_NewEntryDeriv_Large.gifxihttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/CategoryShowingTemplate-large.pngxfhttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/Lexicon_InterliniarAnalyze.gifxdhttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/11/Lexicon_EntrySplit-large.pngxghttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/11/Lexicon_SemanticEntry-Large.pngx_https://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/Lexicon_exportSetup.gifx\https://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/09/ListChoice_Large.pngx[https://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/textchart-large.pngx[https://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/10/FLeX_Notebook-1.pngxZhttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2017/01/CompConc_large.pngxmhttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/11/Lexicon_LexicalRelationMenu-large.pngxfhttps://software.sil.org/fieldworks/wp-content/uploads/sites/38/2016/11/Lexicon_WordListConc-large.pngjcategoriesx)Dictionary,Education,Humanities,Languagesprich_descriptionyFFieldWorks consists of software tools that help you manage linguistic and cultural data. FieldWorks supports tasks ranging from the initial entry of collected data through to the preparation of data for publication, including dictionary development, interlinearization of texts, morphological analysis, and other publications.gversionc9.0¿fapp_idxorg.sil.dictionary-app-builderdnamevDictionary App Buildergsummaryx'Build dictionary apps: pics &amp; audioeiconséxìhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/dictionary-app-builder/069a9c6a397c46f9f2f7fa04e128f212/icons/128x128/org.sil.dictionary-app-builder.pngxÅhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/dictionary-app-builder/069a9c6a397c46f9f2f7fa04e128f212/icons/128x128@2/org.sil.dictionary-app-builder.pngkscreenshotsâxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/dictionary-app-builder/069a9c6a397c46f9f2f7fa04e128f212/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/dictionary-app-builder/069a9c6a397c46f9f2f7fa04e128f212/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/dictionary-app-builder/069a9c6a397c46f9f2f7fa04e128f212/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriestDevelopment,Buildingprich_descriptiony²<em>Dictionary App Builder</em> helps you to build customized dictionary apps for Android and iOS smartphones and tablets. You specify the lexicon data file to use, the app name, fonts, colors, the about box information, the audio, illustrations and the icons. Dictionary App Builder will package everything together and build the customized app for you. You can then install it on your phone, send it to others by Bluetooth, share it on microSD memory cards and publish it to app stores on the Internet.
    gversiond12.3¿fapp_idxorg.sil.keyboard-app-builderdnametKeyboard App Buildergsummaryx Build apps with Keyman keyboardseiconséxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/keyboard-app-builder/b346b3280ce9a875bc3abb08b8b83e55/icons/128x128/org.sil.keyboard-app-builder.pngxïhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/keyboard-app-builder/b346b3280ce9a875bc3abb08b8b83e55/icons/128x128@2/org.sil.keyboard-app-builder.pngkscreenshotsâxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/keyboard-app-builder/b346b3280ce9a875bc3abb08b8b83e55/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/keyboard-app-builder/b346b3280ce9a875bc3abb08b8b83e55/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/keyboard-app-builder/b346b3280ce9a875bc3abb08b8b83e55/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriestDevelopment,Buildingprich_descriptiony▓<em>Keyboard App Builder</em> helps you to build customized keyboard apps for Android smartphones and tablets. A keyboard app allows users to add a system keyboard to their device, enabling them to type in their language within other apps such as Gmail, Facebook and WhatsApp. To build an app, you specify the Keyman keyboard layout files and lexical models to use, the app name, the fonts, the colors, the about box information and the icons. Keyboard App Builder will package everything together and build the customized app for you. You can then install it on your phone, send it to others by Bluetooth, share it on microSD memory cards and publish it to app stores on the Internet.
    gversiond12.3¿fapp_idxorg.sil.reading-app-builderdnamesReading App Buildergsummaryx%Build apps with synced text and audioeiconséxçhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/reading-app-builder/973afaa11e6391467d3b68c13fef6636/icons/128x128/org.sil.reading-app-builder.pngxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/reading-app-builder/973afaa11e6391467d3b68c13fef6636/icons/128x128@2/org.sil.reading-app-builder.pngkscreenshotsâxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/reading-app-builder/973afaa11e6391467d3b68c13fef6636/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/reading-app-builder/973afaa11e6391467d3b68c13fef6636/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sil/reading-app-builder/973afaa11e6391467d3b68c13fef6636/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriestDevelopment,Buildingprich_descriptionyY<em>Reading App Builder</em> helps you build customized apps for smartphones and tablets. You can use it to make apps containing picture books, health and community development materials, song books, illustrated stories and libraries of easy-to-read books for new readers ÔÇô each with the option of synchronizing text and audio, highlighting each phrase as it is read. The app menus, icon, splash screen and colors can all be customized for your language and culture. To build an app, you specify the text and audio files, the app name, the fonts, the colors, the about box information and the icons. Reading App Builder will package everything together and compile the customized app for you. You can then install it on your mobile device, send it to others by Bluetooth, share it on microSD memory cards and publish it to app stores on the Internet.
