3 the distance along the bottom.gversiond28.1¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.ImplodeActivitydnamegImplodegsummaryx9Implode blocks of the same colour until they are all goneeiconséxïhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/ImplodeActivity/935ab3f29b0c6e7352735a3b0b682faf/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.ImplodeActivity.pngxìhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/ImplodeActivity/935ab3f29b0c6e7352735a3b0b682faf/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.ImplodeActivity.pngkscreenshotsüxxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/ImplodeActivity/935ab3f29b0c6e7352735a3b0b682faf/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionxÙImplode is a logic game based on the &quot;falling block&quot; model of Tetris. The game starts with a grid partially filled with blocks. The player makes a move by removing adjacent blocks of the same color in groups of three or more.gversionb20¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.MakeThemFalldnamenMake Them FallgsummaryxIt is a multilevel arcade gameeiconséxàhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.MakeThemFall.pngxçhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.MakeThemFall.pngkscreenshotsàxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/screenshots/image-4_orig.pngxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MakeThemFall/bbaac11627cd39f6d972bfa4a4849f06/screenshots/image-5_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionx Make Them Fall, is a challenging distance game that tests your multitasking skills. Control up to 6 falling stickmen and avoid spikes and obstacles. Choose from six difficulty levels and see how long you can last. Play alone or with friends for added fun!gversiona2¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.MathHurdlerdnamelMath HurdlergsummaryxEngaging math game for childreneiconséxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MathHurdler/17769df292293c906395c49c747e68d5/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.MathHurdler.pngxàhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MathHurdler/17769df292293c906395c49c747e68d5/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.MathHurdler.pngkscreenshotsâxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MathHurdler/17769df292293c906395c49c747e68d5/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MathHurdler/17769df292293c906395c49c747e68d5/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MathHurdler/17769df292293c906395c49c747e68d5/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionxrA game designed to help teach children math in accordance with the Common Core standard for fourth grade students.gversiona4¿fapp_idrorg.sugarlabs.MazednamedMazegsummaryrA simple maze gameeiconséxuhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Maze/c418069088d7cf7050547cf0f6f98b0d/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Maze.pngxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Maze/c418069088d7cf7050547cf0f6f98b0d/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Maze.pngkscreenshotsâxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Maze/c418069088d7cf7050547cf0f6f98b0d/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Maze/c418069088d7cf7050547cf0f6f98b0d/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxmhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Maze/c418069088d7cf7050547cf0f6f98b0d/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptionx}Good at finding your way out of hard situations? Let&apos;s see! Try to make your way through an increasingly difficult path.gversionb32¿fapp_iduorg.sugarlabs.MeasurednamegMeasuregsummaryx5Oscilloscope program for visualizing microphone inputeiconséx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Measure/7baccd9d531d4aa23ed871de0f602178/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Measure.pngx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Measure/7baccd9d531d4aa23ed871de0f602178/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Measure.pngkscreenshotsâxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Measure/7baccd9d531d4aa23ed871de0f602178/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Measure/7baccd9d531d4aa23ed871de0f602178/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Measure/7baccd9d531d4aa23ed871de0f602178/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptiony&Measure is a tool that turns the computer into an oscilloscope. You can easily visualize your voice or even a musical instrument. It provides an interface for the kids to connect with the physical world and an opportunity to view and understand through a visual and statistical representations.gversionc103¿fapp_idvorg.sugarlabs.MemorizednamehMemorizegsummarysFind matching pairseiconséx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Memorize/37df42922949bbc12e33931514b8f0c9/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Memorize.pngxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Memorize/37df42922949bbc12e33931514b8f0c9/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Memorize.pngkscreenshotsâxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Memorize/37df42922949bbc12e33931514b8f0c9/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Memorize/37df42922949bbc12e33931514b8f0c9/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Memorize/37df42922949bbc12e33931514b8f0c9/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptiony1Memorize is about finding matching pairs. A pair can be images, sounds and text and this could be extended to animations or movie snippets as well. Which pairs match is up to the creator of the game. Memorize is more than a predefined game you can play, it allows you to create new games yourself as well.gversionb59ºfapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.MusicBlocksdnamelMusic BlocksgsummaryxNA collection of tools for exploring fundamental musical concepts in a fun way.kscreenshotsüxThttps://github.com/Clue88/musicblocks-launcher/blob/master/screenshot-1.png?raw=truejcategoriesx#Art,ComputerScience,Education,Musicprich_descriptionx>ÔÇ£All musicians are subconsciously mathematiciansÔÇØ ÔÇô Monkgversione3.5.1¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.MusicKeyboarddnamenMusic Keyboardgsummaryx#Play music with this piano keyboardeiconséxçhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MusicKeyboard/e92476a0c920bf7396c334774208e917/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.MusicKeyboard.pngxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MusicKeyboard/e92476a0c920bf7396c334774208e917/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.MusicKeyboard.pngkscreenshotsüxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/MusicKeyboard/e92476a0c920bf7396c334774208e917/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionx¸This activity display a piano keyboard in the screen and can be used to play music selecting sounds from different instruments. In devices with touch screen, can be used touching the screen, in devices without one, the laptop keyboard can be used.gversionb13¿fapp_idsorg.sugarlabs.PaintdnameePaintgsummaryuA sweet painting tooleiconséxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Paint/fcd3ac85bcf0c9d0914966d120893b6b/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Paint.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Paint/fcd3ac85bcf0c9d0914966d120893b6b/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Paint.pngkscreenshotsüxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Paint/fcd3ac85bcf0c9d0914966d120893b6b/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionxàPicasso? Van Gogh? You can be any of them! Just let the artist inside you free. Transform images in your mind to beautiful paintings.gversionb71¿fapp_iduorg.sugarlabs.PhysicsdnamegPhysicsgsummaryxProve Sir Isaac Newton correcteiconséx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Physics/3654b774a0707545ff74f0ea17034b88/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Physics.pngx}https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Physics/3654b774a0707545ff74f0ea17034b88/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Physics.pngkscreenshotsüxphttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Physics/3654b774a0707545ff74f0ea17034b88/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionxzProve Sir Isaac Newton correct. Create real-life simulations using different shapes and see them come to life with forces.gversiond35.1¿fapp_idsorg.sugarlabs.PippydnameePippygsummaryxTalk to your computer in Pythoneiconséxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pippy/29492afb431ba37333fff4c8b1231583/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Pippy.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pippy/29492afb431ba37333fff4c8b1231583/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Pippy.pngkscreenshotsâxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pippy/29492afb431ba37333fff4c8b1231583/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pippy/29492afb431ba37333fff4c8b1231583/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pippy/29492afb431ba37333fff4c8b1231583/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategorieskDevelopmentprich_descriptionyPippy allows the student to examine, execute, and modify simple Python programs. It&apos;s possible to write Python statements to play sounds, calculate expressions, or make simple text based interactive games. It also includes PyGame examples and a tutorial for GTK basics.gversionb76¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.PukllanapacdnamekPukllanapacgsummaryuA sliding-puzzle gameeiconséxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pukllanapac/0913ec39514217e1f3a470f3829a5053/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Pukllanapac.pngxàhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pukllanapac/0913ec39514217e1f3a470f3829a5053/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Pukllanapac.pngkscreenshotsâxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pukllanapac/0913ec39514217e1f3a470f3829a5053/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pukllanapac/0913ec39514217e1f3a470f3829a5053/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Pukllanapac/0913ec39514217e1f3a470f3829a5053/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngjcategoriesdGameprich_descriptiony*Pukllanapac is a sliding-puzzle game. The objective is to rearrange tiles so that all of the circles (and semicircles) are composed of sectors of the same color. There are three different patterns: circles, triangles, and hexagons. Drag tiles to swap their positions. Click on tiles to rotate them.gversionb14¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.ReadETextsdnamekRead ETextsgsummaryxRead thousands of free e-bookseiconséxühttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/ReadETexts/238b1ea81079d694b243abd34fb7a413/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.ReadETexts.pngxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/ReadETexts/238b1ea81079d694b243abd34fb7a413/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.ReadETexts.pngkscreenshotsüxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/ReadETexts/238b1ea81079d694b243abd34fb7a413/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionx┘Read ETexts lets you read all the free e-texts from Project Gutenberg, or use Text to Speech to have them read to you. The built in offline catalog search lets you browse through and download over 30,000 great titles.gversionb28¿fapp_idworg.sugarlabs.SliderulednameiSliderulegsummarywA mechanical calculatoreiconséxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Sliderule/e587683f40a1a0571f381a49cd4a0810/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Sliderule.pngxühttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Sliderule/e587683f40a1a0571f381a49cd4a0810/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Sliderule.pngkscreenshotsüxrhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Sliderule/e587683f40a1a0571f381a49cd4a0810/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionx¾The slide rule also known colloquially as a slipstick, is a mechanical analog computer. Sliderule implements a basic slide rule with C, D, A, and L scales and can be used for multiplication, division, roots, addition and subtraction, and more.gversionb36¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.SolarSystemdnamelSolar SystemgsummarywLearn about the planetseiconséxâhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/SolarSystem/361f9a4b5648af71bdf0cb003376e811/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.SolarSystem.pngxàhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/SolarSystem/361f9a4b5648af71bdf0cb003376e811/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.SolarSystem.pngkscreenshotsüxthttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/SolarSystem/361f9a4b5648af71bdf0cb003376e811/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionxÛThe Solar System activity is a tool to encourage children to learn more about the planets and their moons (natural satellites). It is the author&apos;s hope that this tool serves as a practical and interactve way to explore astronomy.gversiona1¿fapp_idsorg.sugarlabs.SpeakdnameeSpeakgsummaryx.An animated face that speaks whatever you typeeiconséxwhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Speak/fb0a3aaeffca54a936b00fe70f94f1f4/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.Speak.pngxyhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Speak/fb0a3aaeffca54a936b00fe70f94f1f4/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.Speak.pngkscreenshotséxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Speak/fb0a3aaeffca54a936b00fe70f94f1f4/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxnhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/Speak/fb0a3aaeffca54a936b00fe70f94f1f4/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptiony2Speak is a talking face.  Anything you type will be spoken aloud using a speech synthesizer.  You can adjust the accent, rate and pitch of the voice as well as the shape of the eyes and mouth.  This is a great way to experiment with a speech synthesizer, learn to type or just have fun making a funny face.gversionb59¿fapp_idxorg.sugarlabs.StoryActivitydnameeStorygsummarylTell a storyeiconséxçhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/StoryActivity/dcd310ef20e766761af31aed55b2b08b/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.StoryActivity.pngxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/StoryActivity/dcd310ef20e766761af31aed55b2b08b/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.StoryActivity.pngkscreenshotséxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/StoryActivity/dcd310ef20e766761af31aed55b2b08b/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/StoryActivity/dcd310ef20e766761af31aed55b2b08b/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptionx«Story prompts the learner to tell a story by displaying images at random. The learner should try to tell a story that ties the images together into a comprehensive narrative.gversionb20¿fapp_idworg.sugarlabs.SwiftFeetdnamejSwift FeetgsummaryxGet on your feet and dance!eiconséxhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/SwiftFeet/f90472af0972a4472646e44c40a132ee/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.SwiftFeet.pngxühttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/SwiftFeet/f90472af0972a4472646e44c40a132ee/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.SwiftFeet.pngkscreenshotsüxrhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/SwiftFeet/f90472af0972a4472646e44c40a132ee/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriesiEducationprich_descriptiony0A high energy and up-beat action program, Swift Feet encourages children to be active. 20 different exercises and 10 different dances set to music take users through high, moderate and low impact movements. This activity was designed for OLPC Canada in collaboration with ParticipACTION Canada and Ophea.gversiona2¿fapp_idx org.sugarlabs.TurtlePondActivitydnamepTurtle in a Pondgsummaryx0Surround the turtle before it runs of the screeneiconséxæhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/TurtlePondActivity/8c3796bea5e7e4c5ad19281bf59cd6df/icons/128x128/org.sugarlabs.TurtlePondActivity.pngxôhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/TurtlePondActivity/8c3796bea5e7e4c5ad19281bf59cd6df/icons/128x128@2/org.sugarlabs.TurtlePondActivity.pngkscreenshotsüx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/org/sugarlabs/TurtlePondActivity/8c3796bea5e7e4c5ad19281bf59cd6df/screenshots/ima