    gversione4.8.1¿fapp_idxorg.thentrythis.SamplebraindnamekSamplebraingsummaryx2A custom sample mashing app designed by Aphex Twineiconséxçhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/thentrythis/Samplebrain/612be807d8cb852ec3369d5ae5cdfb76/icons/128x128/org.thentrythis.Samplebrain.pngxëhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/thentrythis/Samplebrain/612be807d8cb852ec3369d5ae5cdfb76/icons/128x128@2/org.thentrythis.Samplebrain.pngkscreenshotsüxvhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/org/thentrythis/Samplebrain/612be807d8cb852ec3369d5ae5cdfb76/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngjcategoriespAudioVideo,Musicprich_descriptiony;
      Samplebrain chops samples up into a &apos;brain&apos; of interconnected small sections called blocks which are connected into a network by similarity. It processes a target sample, chopping it up into blocks in the same way, and tries to match each block with one in it&apos;s brain to play in realtime.
