ls of the same color. No attention is paid to the surrounding pixels or to transitions. For certain graphics (mainly pixel art or similar in very low resolution), this may give better results than other methods.gversionc1.3¿fapp_idx+page.codeberg.JakobDev.jdProcessFileWatcherdnametjdProcessFileWatchergsummaryxFEffortlessly monitor and display real-time file access for any processeiconsüxºhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdProcessFileWatcher/fa1f00c05b54db7da00482cd6dc7ec23/icons/128x128/page.codeberg.JakobDev.jdProcessFileWatcher.pngkscreenshotséxåhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdProcessFileWatcher/fa1f00c05b54db7da00482cd6dc7ec23/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxåhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdProcessFileWatcher/fa1f00c05b54db7da00482cd6dc7ec23/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngjcategoriestSystem,Filesystem,Qtprich_descriptionyWith jdProcessFileWatcher, you can monitor all the files accessed by a process. It allows you to start any program and observe in real-time which files it accesses through an easy-to-use GUI. Additionally, you have the option to connect to an already running process.gversionc1.1¿fapp_idx page.codeberg.JakobDev.jdReplacednameijdReplacegsummaryxAWith jdReplace you can replace a text in all files of a directoryeiconséxæhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdReplace/b0554dc4266585b7fa3cfeaf5864232c/icons/128x128/page.codeberg.JakobDev.jdReplace.pngxôhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdReplace/b0554dc4266585b7fa3cfeaf5864232c/icons/128x128@2/page.codeberg.JakobDev.jdReplace.pngkscreenshotsäx~https://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdReplace/b0554dc4266585b7fa3cfeaf5864232c/screenshots/image-1_nl_orig.pngx~https://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdReplace/b0554dc4266585b7fa3cfeaf5864232c/screenshots/image-1_it_orig.pngx{https://dl.flathub.org/media/page/codeberg/JakobDev.jdReplace/b0554dc4266585b7fa3cfeaf5864232c/screenshots/image-1_orig.