    kscreenshotsüxXhttps://gitlab.com/staltz/manyverse-site/-/raw/master/src/images/screenshot-desktop2.pngjcategoriesgNetworkprich_descriptionykManyverse is a decentralized social network. Unlike most social networks today, it is not run by a company which has power over the communications between users. The developers of Manyverse can control the source code to build the app and ship new features, but they have no access to user data. The user has complete ownership and responsibility over their data.gversionm0.2310.9-betaºfapp_idpse.sjoerd.GIScandnamefGIScangsummaryx1Read and analyze GISAXS data stored in cbf formatkscreenshotsäx"http://www.sjoerd.se/giscan_bg.pngx$http://www.sjoerd.se/giscan_main.pngx$http://www.sjoerd.se/giscan_vert.pngx(http://www.sjoerd.se/giscan_settings.pngjcategoriesqEducation,Scienceprich_descriptionyBGIScan is a simple tool to open and analyze data stored in cbf (Crystallographic Binary Format) files. While GIScan is primarily developed with the analyis of GISAXS data in mind, as obtained by the P03 beamline of PETRA III at the DESY Synchrotron in Hamburg, Germany, it should be compatible with any arbitrary cbf data.gversione1.1.6¿fapp_idpse.sjoerd.GraphsdnamefGraphsgsummaryxPlot and manipulate dataeiconséxqhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b6ca6ec760145ad4c37/icons/128x128/se.sjoerd.Graphs.pngxshttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b6ca6ec760145ad4c37/icons/128x128@2/se.sjoerd.Graphs.pngkscreenshotsàxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b6ca6ec760145ad4c37/screenshots/image-1_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b6ca6ec760145ad4c37/screenshots/image-2_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b6ca6ec760145ad4c37/screenshots/image-3_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b6ca6ec760145ad4c37/screenshots/image-4_orig.pngxkhttps://dl.flathub.org/media/se/sjoerd/Graphs/05a67e43f9b32b