b (linked below) and enable it in GNOME Tweaks. In addition to this Flatpak theme, the following components are currently available:gversionc0.1ñfapp_idx#org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Numix-Frost-LightdnamexNumix Frost Light Gtk ThemegsummaryxNumix Frost Light Gtk themeprich_descriptionxBA modern flat theme with a combination of light and dark elements.ñfapp_idxorg.gtk.Gtk3theme.Numix-FrostdnameuNumix Frost Gtk ThemegsummaryuNumix Frost Gtk themeprich_descriptionxBA modern flat theme with a combination of light and dark elements.ñfapp_idworg.gtk.Gtk3theme.NumixdnameoNumix Gtk ThemegsummarykNumix themeprich_descriptionkNumix themeÑfapp_idx"org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-AmberdnamexObsidian-2-Amber Gtk ThemegsummaryvObsidian-2-Amber themeprich_descriptionvObsidian-2-Amber themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx!org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-AquadnamexObsidian-2-Aqua Gtk ThemegsummaryuObsidian-2-Aqua themeprich_descriptionuObsidian-2-Aqua themegversiond2.23Ñfapp_idx!org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-GraydnamexObsidian-2-Gray Gtk ThemegsummaryuObsidian-2-Gray themeprich_descriptionuObsidian-2-Gray themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx"org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-GreendnamexObsidian-2-Green Gtk ThemegsummaryvObsidian-2-Green themeprich_descriptionvObsidian-2-Green themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx#org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-IndigodnamexObsidian-2-Indigo Gtk ThemegsummarywObsidian-2-Indigo themeprich_descriptionwObsidian-2-Indigo themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx!org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-MintdnamexObsidian-2-Mint Gtk ThemegsummaryuObsidian-2-Mint themeprich_descriptionuObsidian-2-Mint themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx#org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-PurplednamexObsidian-2-Purple Gtk ThemegsummarywObsidian-2-Purple themeprich_descriptionwObsidian-2-Purple themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-ReddnamexObsidian-2-Red Gtk ThemegsummarytObsidian-2-Red themeprich_descriptiontObsidian-2-Red themegversiond2.22Ñfapp_idx!org.gtk.Gtk3theme.Obsidian-2-TealdnamexObsidian-2-Teal Gtk ThemegsummaryuObsidian-2-T